data.description: Woo hoo! A must see property! There is an attractive masonry 2 bedroom 2 bath home with 900 sq.ft. mol. Many major updates from 2018-2023: Impact windows thru-out, tankless water heater, interior doors, newer second bath, washer/dryer, stainless appliances, plus central  heat& air, and roof! You will fall in love with the privacy fenced backyard that is a tropical oasis with palm trees and a 30' by 16' inground pool! The 65x134' lot affords room for expanding, a garden and/or yard games! PLUS there's a 300 ft. mol studio/pool house with electric wall heat fireplace, window a/c, fan, wet bar, frig, surround sound--the perfect privacy escape area! BUY it or Tell your friends!! Live the good life with little maintence which affords time to enjoy all that Gulfport has to offer!!
